Item 12. Results of Operations and Financial Condition
        On July 24, 2003, ArQule, Inc. issued a press release announcing its financial results for the second quarter ended June 30, 2003. The press release is furnished as Exhibit 99.1 hereto and incorporated herein by reference.
        Pursuant to the requirements of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934, the Registrant has duly caused this report to be signed on its behalf by the undersigned hereunto duly authorized.
Date: July 28, 2003
