Headings
     12.8. . This Agreement shall inure to the benefit of and be binding upon the parties, their Primary Affiliates, and their respective lawful successors and assigns.
Binding Effect
     12.9. . This Agreement may not be assigned by either party without the prior written consent of the other party, except that either party may assign this Agreement to a successor in connection with the merger, consolidation, spin-off or sale of all or substantially all of its assets or that portion of its business pertaining to the subject matter of this Agreement. Monsanto has the right to extend its rights and benefits under this Agreement to any Primary Affiliate.
Assignment
     12.10. . All notices, requests, demands and other communications required or permitted to be given pursuant to this Agreement shall be in writing and shall be deemed to have been duly given upon the date of receipt if delivered by hand,
