Item 2.02. Results of Operations and Financial Condition.
On April 21, 2005, ArQule, Inc. issued a press release announcing its financial results for the fiscal quarter ended March 31, 2005. The press release is furnished as Exhibit 99.1 hereto and incorporated herein by reference.
Section 9  Financial Statements and Exhibits
