certainties described in ArQule's filings with the Securities and Exchange Commission. Drug development involves a high degree of risk. Only a small number of research and development programs result in the commercialization of a product.  The forward-looking statements contained herein represent the judgment of ArQule as of the date of this report. ArQule disclaims any intent or obligation to update any forward-looking statement except to the extent required by law.
 


