d.
                                     
Extension of Time to Exercise Current Options.
  For a period of twelve (12) months following the Separation Date, the Company shall continue to provide coverage for Employee under its group medical, dental, life and disability insurance policies under the same terms and conditions as other Company employees, including any employee contribution, subject to the applicable plan documents.
