Section 8  Other Events
Item 8.01   Other Events
Richard H. Woodrich, a consultant to ArQule, Inc. (the "Registrant") has been serving as the Registrant's Acting Chief Financial Officer and Treasurer since September 1, 2006. Mr. Woodrich also currently serves as the Registrant's principal financial officer and principal accounting officer for financial reporting purposes. Pending formal action by the Board of Directors of the Registrant regarding a realignment of responsibilities of its finance department, Mr. Woodrich will continue in these roles until on or about August 31, 2007. Mr. Woodrich will continue, as needed, to provide consulting services to the Registrant after August 31, 2007.
During this interim period, Mr. Woodrich will report to Peter S. Lawrence, the Registrant's Executive Vice President, Chief Business Officer, General Counsel and Secretary.  Upon the termination of Mr. Woodrich's service as Acting Chief Financial Officer and Treasurer, the Registrant's financial department will report directly to Mr. Lawrence.
