Governing Law; Venue.
  This Agreement shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the State of Delaware.  The parties agree that any action brought by either party to interpret or enforce any provision of this Agreement shall be brought in, and each party agrees to, and does hereby, submit to the jurisdiction and venue of, the appropriate state or federal court for the district encompassing the Company's principal place of business.
 
c.
            
