Clinical Science Symposium - Oral presentation (with slides) #LBA7502: Results from ARQ 197-209: A global randomized placebo-controlled phase II clinical trial of erlotinib plus ARQ 197 versus erlotinib plus placebo in previously treated EGFR inhibitor-nave patients with locally advanced or metastatic non-small cell lung cancer (NSCLC);
 
                 
