2.
                                      
To approve amendments to the Registrant's Amended and Restated 1994 Equity Incentive Plan to increase the number of shares of common stock available for awards granted under such plan by 3,000,000 from 12,500,000 to 15,500,000 shares of common stock and to incorporate other changes described in the Registrant's proxy statement;
 
3.
                                      
To approve an amendment to the Registrant's Amended and Restated 1996 Employee Stock Purchase Plan to increase the number of shares of common stock available for purchase by participants in such plan by 400,000 from 2,000,000 to 2,400,000 shares of common stock;
 
