Financial Information
 
Item 2.02 Results of Operations and Financial Condition.
 
On May 3, 2012 ArQule, Inc. (the Registrant) issued a press release announcing its financial results for the fiscal quarter ended March 31, 2012.  The press release is furnished as Exhibit 99.1 hereto and incorporated herein by reference.
 
Section 9  Financial Statements and Exhibits
Item 9.01.  Financial Statements and Exhibits.
(d)  Exhibits.
 
 Exhibit 99.1 Text of press release dated May 3, 2012 announcing results of operations.
 
 
