Item 2.02 Results of Operations and Financial Condition.
 
On March 14, 2013, ArQule, Inc. (the Registrant) issued a press release announcing its financial results for the fiscal quarter and year ended December 31, 2012.  The press release is furnished as Exhibit 99.1 hereto and incorporated herein by reference.
 
